title: LIVE: Watch Hurricane Patricia making landfall in Mexico
text:
Hurricane Patricia is making landfall in Mexico, and popular resort towns are in the danger zone.
Patricia is the strongest recorded storm in the Western hemisphere.
Watch the Category 5 story make landfall Friday with this live webcam, which shows the resort area of Ixtapa.
To get the latest on the hurricane, click here .
